productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
My neighbor Betha has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks wide.
I tried to impale it but got fudge all over it.
